<h2>Welcome to PolEval 2020!
<p>PolEval is a <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/SemEval">SemEval</a>-inspired evaluation campaign for natural language processing tools for Polish. Submitted tools compete against one another within certain <a href="@{ListChallengesR}">tasks</a> selected by <a href="/organizers/">organizers</a>, using available data and are evaluated according to pre-established procedures.
<p>Until the end of September 2019 we are collecting tasks to be organized in 2020. Please <a href="mailto:lkobylinski@gmail.com">submit your own task proposal!</a>
